In this statement, the author applauds the Senate for working towards a solution to alleviate the burden of Obamacare on the American people. The administration has consistently tried to repeal and replace Obamacare and hopes that the Senate can pass legislation that addresses the issues caused by Obamacare. The author believes that Obamacare has been disastrous, leading to high healthcare premiums, deductibles, and cancelled or reduced plans. The author emphasizes that inaction is not an option and expresses hope that Senators Graham and Cassidy have found a way to address the Obamacare crisis.